{"tid":2324954,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"MacBook個mon掀起超過某個角度就自動熄左？","createTime":"2020-12-14T10:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T11:25:19.000Z","uid":60347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb7375022d19f89165d411e6ca660d03c2237c1","tid":2324954,"uid":60347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊部2016嘅MacBook Pro，OS都有更到最新<br />\n<br />\n今日成朝早用緊都仲好地地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱想打開嘅時候突然就出現標題提及到嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕輕掀起大概60度以內用係完全正常冇問題着到仲可以教亮度<br />\n但係一過咗嗰個位之後個mon就會突然熄咗<br />\n嗰隻熄咗意思唔係講緊成部機熄咗斷電未開機嗰隻純黑<br />\n而係亮度較到最低但隱隱約約仲見到條Dock或者網頁嗰種暗<br />\n個keyboard同toolbar 都係仲着緊，仲可以㩒制較到亮度不過個mon就完全冇畀反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實在未遇過咁嘅情況，明明冇撞冇跌又冇亂down嘢軟件硬件都諗唔到邊忽出事<br />\n保養又過埋想搵Apple線上支援問都唔畀用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以上嚟問吓有冇巴打都遇過同樣問題或者有冇高人可以指點下<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbccfc14d3ccb575c2aebb8dcf00a750155b1321","tid":2324954,"uid":172629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"開番會唔會話 Your computer restarted because of a problem?"},{"pid":"8aebd85cc6b8bbf692ad73c99f9fc4a85ef44b98","tid":2324954,"uid":63279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb7375022d19f89165d411e6ca660d03c2237c1","tid":2324954,"uid":60347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊部2016嘅MacBook Pro，OS都有更到最新<br />\n<br />\n今日成朝早用緊都仲好地地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱想打開嘅時候突然就出現標題提及到嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕輕掀起大概60度以內用係完全正常冇問題着到仲可以教亮度<br />\n但係一過咗嗰個位之後個mon就